AddNag,provides,a,platform,for,displaying,and,sharing,content,in,mobile,applications,Developers,can,create,nags,simple,pages,that,appear,upon,opening,an,app,that,can,be,used,to,convey,reminders,special,offers,tutorials,etc,AddNag,s,functions,are,available,for,integration,via,API,Further,documentation,can,be,accessed,by,logging,in,to,the,AddNag,website